g2:c.FUNCTION-DEFINITION.g2:a.TEXT: _opcs-check-for-opac () = (if there exists a module-information MI such that (the top-level-module of MI = the symbol opac) then true else false)

g2:c.PROCEDURE.g2:a.TEXT: get-root-node(object-manager-configuration-name: symbol, DisplayString: text) = (structure) begin return structure(CATEGORY: the symbol ROOT, SPECIFIER: object-manager-configuration-name, DISPLAY-STRING: DisplayString, IS-LEAF: false); end

collect-palette-description-if-it-exists(CurrentPaletteDescriptions: sequence, PaletteType: symbol, PaletteLabel: text, PaletteKeyOrProcedure: symbol) = (sequence)
begin case (PaletteType) of CHOICE-TEMPLATE: if there exists an item named by PaletteKeyOrProcedure then CurrentPaletteDescriptions = insert-at-end(CurrentPaletteDescriptions, structure(TYPE: paletteType, LABEL: PaletteLabel, KEY: PaletteKeyOrProcedure)); end; case (PaletteType) of CASCADE-TEMPLATE: if there exists a procedure named by PaletteKeyOrProcedure then CurrentPaletteDescriptions = insert-at-end(CurrentPaletteDescriptions, structure(TYPE: paletteType, LABEL: PaletteLabel, KEY: PaletteKeyOrProcedure)); end; return CurrentPaletteDescriptions; end

get-module-prefix(ModuleName: symbol) = (text) MI: class opcsrui-module-storage-information; begin if there exists a opcsrui-module-storage-information MI such that (the opcsrui-module-name of MI = ModuleName) then return the opcsrui-module-prefix of MI end
